des: "Great as a dry rub for pork or chicken, or added to your favorite BBQ sauce to add a bit of kick and flavor to your basting. I prefer to rub my pork the day before and refrigerate it overnight wrapped tight in plastic wrap. Also a good seasoning for eggs!"
ins: Mix brown sugar, paprika, kosher salt, white sugar, chili powder, beef bouillon, garlic powder, onion powder, black pepper, cayenne pepper, and tarragon leaves together in an airtight container. Store in a cool, dark place.
